  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Currently there is no way to query the block reward for a given address and block. If one want's to know how much reward he got out of the block the individual rewards (miner, tx fees & uncles) have to be calculated manually which is cumbersome and error prone.\n\nIt would be good to have the following api call:\neth_getReward(address, block)\n\nIt should return the amount of Wei rewarded to this address from the block or 0 if the address received 0 rewards.\n",
